                <note rend="inline" type="source">125.351/10–2649: Circular telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to <gloss
                            type="to">Certain Diplomatic and Consular Offices in China</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-10-26T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 26, 1949—5 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Consulate Dairen closed Oct 21. All Amer personnel departed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
